INTRODUCTION
Play Jewel Block Puzzle on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Jewel Block Puzzle extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Jewel Block Puzzle icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Jewel Block Puzzle popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

HOW TO PLAY?
Save all of them to win the game
